Key Match Events: The Orioles won 5-4 in 11 innings against the Rays, securing a two-game lead over the Rays for first place in the AL East.
Post-Match Reflections: The Orioles secured their first playoff spot since 2016.
The Orioles ended a seven-year playoff drought, making the postseason for the first time since 2016.
The race for both the AL East and the number one seed in the AL playoff picture is still ongoing between the Orioles and Rays.
